annotation.value: Mostly acreage. Most of this area is occupied by Car Barns and a nursery. Due to the gradual doing away of street cars in the city, which are now being supplanted by buses, it is possible these car barns may be removed. However, this area will never be desirable for residential purposes as long as the coal mine to the east continues to operate.
